Key GPT-4 Vision Features
1. Multimodal Translation
Analyzes manga panels as images to understand visual context
Identifies character expressions, scene mood, and action
Uses visual cues to improve translation accuracy
2. Context Memory System
Maintains narrative continuity across panels (last 5 panels)
Preserves character voice consistency
Tracks emotional arcs through scenes
3. Advanced Capabilities
Streaming: Real-time translation updates for UI feedback
Cultural consultation: Explains references and wordplay
Vision analysis: JSON-structured panel understanding
Cost tracking: Per-request cost calculation and budgeting
4. Manga-Specific Optimizations
Specialized system prompts for anime/manga translation
SFX handling with visual context
Honorifics preservation with personality awareness
Character voice consistency across panels
5. Resilience
Automatic fallback to cheaper models (gpt-4o-mini) on quota issues
Retry logic with exponential backoff
Context window management for long conversations

Usage Examples

// Basic translation
const result = await openaiGPT.translate("お前はもう死んでいる", {
  sourceLang: "ja",
  targetLang: "en",
  sceneContext: "dramatic confrontation"
});
// Returns: { text: "You're already dead", confidence: 0.95, cost: 0.002 }

// With image context (GPT-4 Vision)
const panelResult = await openaiGPT.translateWithVision(
  "どうしたの？",
  imageBase64,
  {
    analyzeFirst: true, // Analyze image before translating
    characterContext: { name: "Naruto", personality: "energetic" }
  }
);

// Streaming for real-time display
await openaiGPT.translateStreaming("長いテキスト...", {}, (chunk, full) => {
  updateUI(full); // Update translation as it arrives
});

// Cultural explanation
const culture = await openaiGPT.explainCulturalContext("桜の季節", "ja");
// Returns cultural context about cherry blossom season symbolism

his adapter provides the highest quality translations by understanding visual context, maintaining narrative continuity, and leveraging GPT-4's superior reasoning for complex cultural nuances.